overview:
Ensign Technologies LLC is a technology consulting and services company. Ensign Tech works with small businesses and startups from one person to hundreds of employees to improve business processes, technology infrastructure, and marketing (social media, websites, word of mouth, and some traditional advertising).

Ensign Tech also has a home technology division that focuses on enthusiast technology products and services for the home.

Ensign Tech pulls together professionals from a wide variety of disciplines, including hardware, software development, web development, design, and networking, among others. They provide managed IT services, outsourced IT support, network security, data backup, and technology leasing programs to help companies focus on innovation. Ensign Tech’s goal is to provide world class IT service to small business.
